schools.name: The Early Lrn Center At George Earle

data.description: This 3 bed, 1 bath ranch sits on a .25 acre, corner lot. The property is located in Hobart township. There's a 2.5 car garage with a paved driveway and ample paved parking space. There's a covered front porch and an above ground pool with deck in the backyard. The roof is about 3 years old. The living room, kitchen, bathroom, and laundry room have ceramic tile flooring. The bedrooms have hardwood flooring. The kitchen appliances, washer, and dryer are included.
